      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>The story about the Desert Dragon and Cassius is nearing the end... How did you find it so far?<BR>Did their story interest you?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
