   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>You still have more to find out. The reason why the Desert Dragon remained in her jewel form for so long has not been revealed yet.<BR>Go on now once again to Memoria...<BR>
 <BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>* A party of 4 is recommended for Memoria</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n749_night_kasius-1" image="QN_Npc_hero_Casius.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius${sound:npc_Casius_qu_4279_07.ogg}<BR>Do you think I still have the chance to get her heart back?<BR>I look pathetic to be clinging onto this vague hope.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Cassius stares at the direction where Aisha disappeared to with a perplexed face)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n750_night_kasius-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius$<BR>Aisha. Am I so undeserving of your trust?<BR>I thought at least you would........</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n750_night_kasius-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n750_night_kasius-2-a" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius$<BR>She hesitated at the last moment.<BR>She couldn't bear to harm me. What could have happened if I stopped at that split second?<BR>If I stopped... She would still be by my side… Alive…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n750_night_kasius-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n750_night_kasius-2-b" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius${sound:npc_Casius_qu_4280_01.ogg}<BR>But I didn't stop, and my sword pierced her.<BR>I always talked to her about how great love was, but I didn't practice what I preached.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n750_night_kasius-2-b" image="QN_Npc_hero_Casius.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n750_night_kasius-2-c" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius${sound:npc_Casius_qu_4280_02.ogg}<BR>In the end, I couldn't trust nor love her.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Cassius looks at his sword)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n750_night_kasius-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n750_night_kasius-2-d" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius${sound:npc_Casius_qu_4280_03.ogg}<BR>Thank you for following this foolish king until here.<BR>My loyal friend.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n750_night_kasius-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n750_night_kasius-2-e" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius${sound:npc_Casius_qu_4280_04.ogg}<BR>I'm thankful that you have survived till the end, even when you were with a foolish king like me.<BR>…But everything is over now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n750_night_kasius-2-e" image="QN_Npc_hero_Casius.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n750_night_kasius-3" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius${sound:npc_Casius_qu_4280_05.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Cassius looks around at the desolate battlefield)<BR></FONT>Go now.<BR>I will bury all that has happened here in my memory. I hope you will forget everything you saw here too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n750_night_kasius-3" image="QN_Npc_hero_Casius.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Knight King Cassius$<BR>Aisha....<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Cassius gazes far away.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>There are no signs of the dragon in any part of the vast desert)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-a" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Tell her about the story.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>Oh you're back. You look perplexed.<BR>It was but an old memory that you saw… But you look like you just lost an old friend.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-b" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well… I don't know.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-b" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Isn't it due to a lack of trust?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-b" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Keep quiet)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Madeleine nods her head after hearing the story)<BR></FONT>I see. A love story between a human and a non-human....<BR>As far as I know, those cases don't have a happy ending. What do you think is the reason?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-c" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>…Even they themselves didn't know the answer, so any reason would only be a guess.<BR>Here is a reward for following an old story until the end.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-d" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
