   <talk_paragraph index="n776_darklair_mardlen-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Priestess of Darkness Madeleine$<BR>This is what King Cassius always kept with him to give Aisha.<BR>
It is said that he gave it to his soldier who had survived with him until the end.<BR>Maybe that was you....<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Madeleine looks at you with her mystical eyes)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
